data.description: Beautiful 4-bedroom 3-bathroom home in Aliante Master Association. One mile North of the 215 freeway - Target, Walmart, Costco and much more shopping. Kitchen includes upgraded countertops, stainless steel fridge and dishwasher. Beautiful new wood laminate flooring downstairs. Ceiling fans in bedrooms and back patio. Security system, soft water system and RO are all owned. Upstairs AC is less than 3 yrs old.Must see!!!
